data.description: Beautifully renovated house in old town. 2 bedroom 2 bathroom with a loft in the heart of Key West. Square footage does not include additional loft area.  Located in X Flood Zone. Walk into a shot gun style house down a long hallway. Off the hallway is a bedroom with bathroom en suite, then the guest bathroom, and finally guest bedroom. At the end of the hallway is a kitchen. In the kitchen there are sliding glass doors that open up to back porch with a small yard. There is a washer and dryer outside on back porch. Front porch is great for people watching.
